advisories.title: Prototype Pollution in async
advisories.description: A vulnerability exists in Async through 3.2.1 for 3.x and through 2.6.3 for 2.x (fixed in 3.2.2 and 2.6.4), which could let a malicious user obtain privileges via the `mapValues()` method.
